'''Nathan L. Segerlind''' ([[December]], [[1973]]) is the author of the text adventure parody ''[[The Bridge of Catzad-Dum]]''<ref>[http://www.lysator.liu.se/tolkien-games/entry/catzad-dum.html Tolkien Games] (retrieved 4 December 2010)</ref><ref>[http://www.meristation.com/v3/des_articulo.php?pic=CON&id=2254&idj=&idp=&tipo=art&c=1&pos=5 Meristation, El Anillo interactivo] p. 6 (retrieved 4 December 2010)</ref> and eight other adventures for the ''[[Eamon (video game)|Eamon]]'' series.
